name: Experiment Or Die #10
description: Known as the Box Heroes, for years my friends and I would don hand painted costume suits made completely out of corrugated cardboard and amongst other things, would walk in the Dragon Con parade every year. They are hot, uncomfortable, and depending on how much you sweat, they often didn't make it the entire day intact. My wife eventually joined in the fun and we even won a Halloween costume contest wearing our Zombie Box Hero Suits. So despite winning, and the fact that I can't actually see her face... I'm not sure if this bird is serious or sarcastic. IG: Nikejerk
